"\"sec.filesystems.major.btrfs.quota\"/> . <!--Quotas for Btrfs partitions "
"are handled differently and cannot be enabled in the &yast; Expert "
"Partitioner.--> <remark>taroth 2014-06-04: todo - after btrfs quotas have "
